inson\", \"score\": 0.9909022562059204, \"rank\": 0.009181272660502861, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1451, \"end\": 1458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9300443415000067, \"rank\": 0.07521729615798864, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old is favourite for 800m glory, particularly with Athing Mu not in Paris, and Hodgkinson goes in the fourth heat this evening.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1530, \"end\": 1539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athing_Mu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Athing Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athing_Mu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athing_Mu\"}, {\"begin\": 1547, \"end\": 1552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3426135987688873e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1558, \"end\": 1568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9909022562059204, \"rank\": 0.009181272660502861, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fellow Brits Phoebe Gill and Jemma Reekie are also involved.\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1621, \"end\": 1627, \"title\": \"